<li id='fn-3121-21'> Wordseer, &#8220;Search Slave Narratives,&#8221; University of California at Berkeley, <a href="http://wordseer.berkeley.edu/slave_narratives/" target="_blank">http://wordseer.berkeley.edu/slave_narratives/</a>. <span class='footnotereverse'><a href='#fnref-3121-21'>&#8617;</a></span></li>
<li id='fn-3121-22'> Mapping the Republic of Letters, Stanford University, <a href="https://republicofletters.stanford.edu/#maps" target="_blank">https://republicofletters.stanford.edu/#maps</a>. <span class='footnotereverse'><a href='#fnref-3121-22'>&#8617;</a></span></li>
<li id='fn-3121-23'> Thinkmap, <em>Visual Thesaurus</em>, <a href="http://www.visualthesaurus.com/" target="_blank">http://www.visualthesaurus.com/</a>. <span class='footnotereverse'><a href='#fnref-3121-23'>&#8617;</a></span></li>
<li id='fn-3121-24'> Moritz Stefaner, <em>Vizosphere</em>, <a href="http://www.visualizing.org/full-screen/29391" target="_blank">http://www.visualizing.org/full-screen/29391</a>. <span class='footnotereverse'><a href='#fnref-3121-24'>&#8617;</a></span></li>
<li id='fn-3121-25'> Nathan Yau, Flowing Data, http://flowingdata.com; PeopleMovin: Migration flows across the world, <a href="http://peoplemov.in/" target="_blank">http://peoplemov.in/</a>. <span class='footnotereverse'><a href='#fnref-3121-25'>&#8617;</a></span></li>
</ol>
</div>



	


	


